      <p class="meta">Publicado em 2026-04-02 11:10:52</p>
      <figure class="post-thumb"><img src="https://fasgoncalves.github.io/fragmentoscaos-img/imagens/file_00000000c780724390dde69ada339bfb.jpg" alt=""></figure>
